interrupt-event-signal
    Move interrupt event signal code common to Kochab and Rigel into its own component.

sem-max-init
    Support optional configuration of semaphore limits that cause a fatal error if exceeded.

arm-kochab-preempt
    Merge back redesigned armv7m preemption mechanism for Kochab from SMACCM development head.

lock-wait-timeouts
    Implement timeout versions of mutex_lock and sem_wait using the existing timer framework.
